1
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,280
Gu Zhantian

2
00:01:23,439 --> 00:01:24,519
Stop playing dead.

3
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:25,879
Get him!

4
00:01:45,159 --> 00:01:46,280
Why?

5
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,280
I suddenly can't sense

6
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,879
my connection to this world.

7
00:01:49,319 --> 00:01:50,959
The power I've accumulated for so long...

8
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,079
It was all for today.

9
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:54,439
Not used to losing control, are you?

10
00:01:57,079 --> 00:01:57,959
Gu Zhantian.

11
00:01:58,439 --> 00:01:59,480
In my world,

12
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:01,040
you are always the winner.

13
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,760
Power, wealth, women...

14
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:05,079
You can have whatever you want.

15
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,079
Why?

16
00:02:06,079 --> 00:02:08,039
Why did you betray me?

17
00:02:08,319 --> 00:02:09,120
Master.

18
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:10,000
I didn't expect

19
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,240
you to be the Heavenly Dao.

20
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:14,280
What gives you the right to control my life?

21
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:16,719
But you are all characters in a novel.

22
00:02:16,719 --> 00:02:17,879
It's destined.

23
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:20,080
This is the Mandate of Heaven.

24
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,479
Bullshit Mandate of Heaven!

25
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,759
Whether I'm the protagonist

26
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:23,560
or a supporting character

27
00:02:23,639 --> 00:02:25,240
is not up to you to decide.

28
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,199
My life

29
00:02:27,199 --> 00:02:29,039
is meant to defy the heavens and change my fate.

30
00:02:29,319 --> 00:02:30,319
Don't forget,

31
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:32,479
this is the setting you gave me.

32
00:02:47,759 --> 00:02:48,560
Liu Jie,

33
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:50,039
let's give it one last shot.

34
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:43,680
Ultimate kill!

35
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,159
Beautiful!

36
00:03:45,719 --> 00:03:47,080
As the child of the Mandate of Heaven,

37
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,479
how can you defy the heavens?

38
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,479
Gu Zhantian,

39
00:03:49,479 --> 00:03:51,159
just be my vessel obediently.

40
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:02,680
In your dreams!

41
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:04,240
Xue Ning,

42
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,240
do it now!

43
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,240
Yes!

44
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,080
Well done!

45
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,479
Young Master,

46
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:16,560
you go first.

47
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,319
Xue Ning will join you later.

48
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,160
You want to die?

49
00:04:25,879 --> 00:04:27,839
Let me grant your wish.

50
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:34,680
Lu Chengwen,

51
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,920
don't let him pull the sword out!

52
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,839
Got it!

53
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,040
If I die,

54
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,639
you will all disappear!

55
00:04:50,079 --> 00:04:51,040
Even if I die,

56
00:04:51,319 --> 00:04:52,879
I won't be a puppet!

57
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:12,839
Ahhh!

58
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,360
Young Master!

59
00:05:31,079 --> 00:05:31,920
We succeeded.

60
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,480
I can finally return

61
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,639
to the real world.

62
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,240
I really want to know

63
00:05:40,079 --> 00:05:42,519
what the real world is actually like.

64
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,720
In the next life,

65
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,519
take me there.

66
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,439
It's pretty much like here.

67
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,920
It's just that

68
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,879
there are no Gods of War.

69
00:05:59,879 --> 00:06:00,879
Farewell,

70
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,480
Brother.

71
00:06:09,879 --> 00:06:11,160
This world is about to collapse.

72
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,120
I'll take you away.

73
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:28,279
Chengwen

74
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:28,680
Brother Chengwen

75
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,519
Wake up.

76
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:30,879
Are you okay?

77
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:35,759
Brother Chengwen.

78
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:36,920
Chengwen.

79
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,639
Brother Chengwen.

80
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:38,480
Brother Chengwen.

81
00:06:38,519 --> 00:06:39,319
Mr. Lu.

82
00:06:39,319 --> 00:06:39,920
Thank goodness.

83
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,839
You're all okay.

84
00:06:43,759 --> 00:06:44,639
Brother Chengwen.

85
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,519
Lu Chengwen.

86
00:06:46,519 --> 00:06:47,480
If you hadn't come to,

87
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:49,079
we wouldn't have had time to say goodbye.

88
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:50,439
Say goodbye?

89
00:06:50,439 --> 00:06:51,160
Yes.

90
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,480
Our world

91
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,839
is collapsing and disappearing.

92
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,519
We are one with it.

93
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,680
So...

94
00:06:56,879 --> 00:06:57,879
So annoying.

95
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:59,240
We don't have enough time as it is,

96
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,639
and we still have to say so much.

97
00:07:00,879 --> 00:07:01,839
Brother Chengwen,

98
00:07:02,519 --> 00:07:04,319
I will never forget you.

99
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:06,240
You can't forget me either.

100
00:07:13,319 --> 00:07:14,120
Mr. Lu,

101
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:16,240
I hope I can stay by your side in the next life

102
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,519
to repay your kindness.

103
00:07:22,439 --> 00:07:23,240
Chengwen,

104
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:24,879
thank you

105
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:27,639
for letting us in this cycle

106
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:30,160
have a different experience.

107
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,360
Brother Chengwen,

108
00:07:42,879 --> 00:07:44,319
thank you

109
00:07:44,319 --> 00:07:46,360
for letting me experience the most sincere feelings.

110
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:48,920
Goodbye.

111
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,040
Thank you all

112
00:08:15,879 --> 00:08:18,240
for giving me

113
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,959
a brief but warm memory.

114
00:08:23,759 --> 00:08:24,560
Farewell.

115
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:28,639
What farewell?

116
00:08:31,079 --> 00:08:33,120
The old novel world has collapsed.

117
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,600
A new novel world with you as the protagonist

118
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,559
is forming.

119
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:39,080
I am the Heavenly Dao of the new world.

120
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,159
Forget it.

121
00:08:46,159 --> 00:08:48,279
I still need to take this money and medicine

122
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:49,240
back to save my mom.

123
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,639
What if I told you

124
00:08:51,639 --> 00:08:53,080
that was all a lie?

125
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,480
How could the money and medicine here

126
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:56,519
save someone in the real world?

127
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:00,879
You sneaky old Six.

128
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,679
I knew you were lying to me.

129
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,559
But going back alive...

130
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:05,559
That wasn't a lie, right?

131
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,639
Stay.

132
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:08,879
Here,

133
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:10,840
all four of them will fight to love you.

134
00:09:10,879 --> 00:09:12,960
Your family here will also give you warmth.

135
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:13,519
The Lu family

136
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:15,639
will become the richest family ruling Haicheng.

137
00:09:15,879 --> 00:09:17,480
The whole world will revolve around you.

138
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:18,639
Forget it.

139
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:20,639
I don't have

140
00:09:20,639 --> 00:09:22,240
the habit of controlling others' fates.

141
00:09:22,519 --> 00:09:23,159
Everyone has

142
00:09:23,159 --> 00:09:24,840
the right to choose how they live.

143
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:26,080
And I don't want

144
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:28,120
them to become fuel for my story.

145
00:09:28,759 --> 00:09:30,080
You better think this through.

146
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,639
If you leave,

147
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,639
you'll have nothing.

148
00:09:34,759 --> 00:09:35,879
So be it.

149
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:36,960
Anyway,

150
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,840
in that world,

151
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,080
I'm just a

152
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:39,879
nobody.

153
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,240
But

154
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:45,440
I have the right to live freely.

155
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:46,440
Haha.

156
00:09:46,639 --> 00:09:47,440
Lu Chengwen,

157
00:09:47,879 --> 00:09:49,440
you are truly interesting.

158
00:09:49,679 --> 00:09:51,480
Without your will to support it,

159
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:53,840
the new novel world can't form either.

160
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,240
But this time,

161
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,639
I really have to go.

162
00:09:56,879 --> 00:09:57,799
I'm very glad

163
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:58,639
that on this journey,

164
00:09:58,639 --> 00:09:59,639
I traveled with you.

165
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:00,879
Bye-bye,

166
00:10:00,879 --> 00:10:01,639
Liu Ye.

167
00:10:26,759 --> 00:10:27,279
Are you blind?

168
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:28,159
Watch where you're going!

169
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,120
Thank God.

170
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:36,919
That was a close call.

171
00:10:41,639 --> 00:10:42,240
Hello?

172
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:42,879
Dr. Li.

173
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:44,279
Did something happen to my mom?

174
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:45,879
No, no.

175
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,080
Congratulations.

176
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,519
Your mother's illness

177
00:10:48,519 --> 00:10:49,759
has just been cured by the National Academy of Sciences.

178
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:51,879
An academician named Gu made the breakthrough.

179
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:52,759
Right now, they

180
00:10:52,759 --> 00:10:54,440
are recruiting clinical trial participants.

181
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:55,440
The treatment is free.

182
00:10:55,639 --> 00:10:57,039
You should go sign up right away.

183
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:00,919
That's great!

184
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,480
Thank you, Dr. Li.

185
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:03,679
I'll be right there.

186
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:21,919
Chengwen.

187
00:11:24,559 --> 00:11:25,360
Mom.

188
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,039
You're awake.

189
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:29,639
I'm not having the surgery.

190
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,840
Don't push yourself too hard.

191
00:11:37,879 --> 00:11:38,639
Mom,

192
00:11:38,639 --> 00:11:40,080
the surgery is already done.

193
00:11:40,159 --> 00:11:41,039
It was very successful.

194
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:43,320
The hospital even helped us apply for free treatment.

195
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:45,440
You're completely fine now.

196
00:11:45,759 --> 00:11:46,639
All you need to do now

197
00:11:46,639 --> 00:11:48,240
is rest and recover.

198
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,919
Is that really true?

199
00:11:49,919 --> 00:11:50,720
Yes.

200
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:09,440
A few months have passed in a flash.

201
00:12:09,679 --> 00:12:11,120
It feels so unreal.

202
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,960
Did I really go to that world?

203
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,639
Maybe

204
00:12:16,639 --> 00:12:18,080
it was just a dream.
